text: KNHM (91.5 FM) is a radio station licensed to Bayside, California. The station is owned by Southern Oregon University, and is an affiliate of Jefferson Public Radio, airing JPR's "News & Information" service, consisting of news and talk programming. ==External links== *ijpr.org NHM Category:NPR member stations Category:Radio stations established in 1995 Category:1995 establishments in California Category:Southern Oregon University
